== Appeals ==
For disciplinary action less than banning, an appeal can be made wherein Wiki Maintainers can collectively review the situation and either uphold it or reverse it. In the event it is upheld, an appeal can still be made to VRChat Staff by [https://help.vrchat.com/hc/en-us/requests/new?ticket_form_id=1500000182242 using this form]. Their final decision takes precedence.